oneInt

oneInt.Rd

A simulated dataset based on the elementary interaction model.

Examples


m1 <- "
# Outer Model
  X =~ x1 + x2 + x3
  Z =~ z1 + z2 + z3
  Y =~ y1 + y2 + y3
# Inner Model
  Y ~ X + Z + X:Z
"

est <- modsem(m1, data = oneInt)
summary(est)
